            h1 Course Layout
            h5 Courses are structured based on their heading and position in the table associated with that heading. When you add a course it must be entered with a heading so that the program knows where you want that course to be in the Program Of Study. This page allows you to view all available courses in the system and change their table based on heading. And you can change which position in that table you wish the course to be in.
