          .col-md-6(style='padding-top:5%;')
            h1 Course Layout
            h5 The Last two columns are used to define where courses will live in the Program Of Study. The Position is the position in the table. The tables start at 1 and courses can be disabled/removed from a catalog-year-table by setting their positions to 0. Headings are the names of the table headings where you can choose which table you wish that course to live in.

